<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 15:14:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西方消息人士称，伊朗的核飞跃“极其严重”，损害了外交</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-nuclear-leap-extremely-serious-hurts-diplomacy-western-source-says-2024-12-07/</link><description>一位西方外交消息人士周六表示，伊朗加速浓缩铀至接近炸弹级别的行为“极其严重”，没有民事理由，并且与德黑兰希望进行认真核谈判的说法相矛盾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 14:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-nuclear-leap-extremely-serious-hurts-diplomacy-western-source-says-2024-12-07/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯石油沙皇称特朗普捍卫美国生产商的举措“合适”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-oil-tsar-says-trumps-moves-defend-us-producers-fitting-2024-12-07/</link><description>俄罗斯最大石油生产商俄罗斯石油公司(Rosneft)总裁伊戈尔·谢钦(Igor Sechin)周六表示，他批准美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)保护国内能源生产商的提议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 13:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-oil-tsar-says-trumps-moves-defend-us-producers-fitting-2024-12-07/</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，墨西哥竭尽全力保护与美国、加拿大的贸易协定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-doing-all-it-can-protect-trade-agreement-with-us-canada-official-says-2024-12-06/</link><description>墨西哥对来自亚洲的走私货物发起打击，查获了创纪录数量的芬太尼，并拘留了数千名移民。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 18:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-doing-all-it-can-protect-trade-agreement-with-us-canada-official-says-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>法院做出不利于 TikTok 的裁决后，接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-happens-next-tiktok-after-court-ruling-against-it-2024-12-06/</link><description>在禁令于 1 月 19 日生效之前，可以就这一裁决向最高法院提出上诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 17:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-happens-next-tiktok-after-court-ruling-against-it-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国上诉法院对 TikTok 重磅裁决的关键引述</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/key-quotes-us-appeals-courts-blockbuster-tiktok-ruling-2024-12-06/</link><description>美国联邦上诉法院周五维持了一项可能迫使中国字节跳动在美国出售其短视频应用 TikTok 的法律。以下是这项轰动一时的裁决中的一些关键段落，该裁决驳回了有关该法律将侵犯美国宪法第一修正案言论保护的说法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/key-quotes-us-appeals-courts-blockbuster-tiktok-ruling-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国上诉法院维持强制出售 TikTok 的法律</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-appeals-court-upholds-tiktok-law-forcing-its-sale-2024-12-06/</link><description>美国联邦上诉法院周五维持了一项法律，要求中国字节跳动在明年初之前在美国剥离其流行的短视频应用 TikTok，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 15:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-appeals-court-upholds-tiktok-law-forcing-its-sale-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，育碧股东正在就可能的收购条款进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubisoft-shareholders-talks-over-possible-buyout-terms-sources-say-2024-12-06/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，育碧娱乐公司的股东正在考虑如何在不减少创始家族控制权的情况下对《刺客信条》视频游戏制造商进行可能的收购。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 14:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubisoft-shareholders-talks-over-possible-buyout-terms-sources-say-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>京东物流8.92亿美元收购跨粤快递全资股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jd-logistics-buy-remaining-stake-kuayue-express-892-mln-2024-12-06/</link><description>物流服务公司周五表示，中国京东物流将以不超过 64.8 亿元人民币（8.92 亿美元）的价格收购其尚未持有的跨越快递集团 36.43% 的股权，以进一步增强快递服务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jd-logistics-buy-remaining-stake-kuayue-express-892-mln-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>西方国家对中国感到不安，忙于重组关键矿产供应链</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rattled-by-china-west-scrambles-rejig-critical-minerals-supply-chains-2024-12-06/</link><description>中国对战略矿产的贸易限制开始打击西方公司的痛处。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rattled-by-china-west-scrambles-rejig-critical-minerals-supply-chains-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>网上对中国经济的两种批评观点在政策会议前消失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-critical-online-views-chinas-economy-vanish-ahead-policy-meeting-2024-12-06/</link><description>一位著名经济学家对中国消费疲软、失业和“沮丧”的年轻人的悲观评论在社交媒体上疯传，但现在已经从中国严格控制的互联网上消失了。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:27:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-critical-online-views-chinas-economy-vanish-ahead-policy-meeting-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回活动人士根据新国安法提早获释的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-activists-bid-early-release-under-new-security-law-2024-12-06/</link><description>周五，香港一家法院驳回了一名根据中国国安法因分裂国家罪入狱的活动人士提出的提早出狱的上诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-activists-bid-early-release-under-new-security-law-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>NBA将重返中国 与澳门签订多年合约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</link><description>美国国家篮球协会(NBA)签署了一份多年期协议，从2025年起在澳门举行季前赛，这标志着该联盟在2019年香港抗议活动引发争议后阔别中国市场多年后重返中国市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>在预期的战争游戏之前，台湾敦促中国“松开拳头”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周五敦促中国“松开拳头”，不要采取任何单方面行动，并在预计中国将在台湾举行军演之前表示，北京不会通过军事演习赢得任何尊重。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾在南海对峙后与盟友举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</link><description>菲律宾军方周五表示，菲律宾与美国和日本在南海专属经济区内举行海上演习，两天前，菲律宾与北京围绕争议浅滩发生海上对峙。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国新疆棉花协会呼吁国际品牌恢复棉花使用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-xinjiang-cotton-association-calls-international-brands-restore-cotton-use-2024-12-06/</link><description>中国新疆棉花协会表示，国际品牌应该对新疆棉花给予“充分尊重和信任”，此前一名高管上周发表评论称服装公司优衣库不从该地区采购供应。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-xinjiang-cotton-association-calls-international-brands-restore-cotton-use-2024-12-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>